                    "game-id": "978beb291b7b1c2b3bd65e46fa769e12",
                    "text": "Aquatic creatures are at home underwater. Their bludgeoning and slashing unarmed Strikes don\u2019t take the usual \u20132 penalty for being underwater. Aquatic creatures can breathe water but not air.",
